4879	<html>\n   <head>\n     <!-- Solar system: /static/main/images/solarsystem.jpg -->\n     <style>\n        body {\n           background-image: url(/static/main/images/solarsystem.jpg);\n           background-size: cover;\n           background-position: center;\n        }\n        table{\n        margin: 0 auto;\n        background:rgba(225,225,225,0.5);\n        font-size:30px;\n        }\n        input{\n            text-align:center;\n        }\n        h1,h2{background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);\n        }\n        h1{\n            text-align:center;\n        }\n     </style>\n   </head>\n   <body>\n       <h1>Kila sayari ina miezi mingapi?</h1>\n       <table>\n<tr><th>Sayari</th><th>Miezi Mingapi</th></tr>\n<tr><td>Mercury</td><td><input value="0"></td>\n<tr><td>Venus</td><td><input value="0"></td>\n<tr><td>Earth</td><td><input value="1"></td>\n<tr><td>Mars</td><td><input value="2"></td>\n<tr><td>Jupiter</td><td><input value="67"></td>\n<tr><td>saturn</td><td><input value="62"></td>\n<tr><td>Uranus</td><td><input value="27"></td>\n<tr><td>Neptune</td><td><input value="14"></td>\n<tr><td>Pluto</td><td><input value="5"></td>\n</table>\n<br>\n<center><button id='calculate'>HESABU JUMLA</button></center>\n<center><h2>Jumla ya miezi:<span id="output"></span></h2></center>\n     <script>\n       document.getElementById('calculate').onclick = function() {\n         var inputs = document.getElementsByTagName("input");\n         var sum=0;\n         Array.prototype.forEach.call(inputs, function(input, index, arr) {\n             sum+=parseInt(input.value)\n         });\n         var output = document.getElementById("output");\n         output.innerText=sum\n       };\n     </script>\n   </body>\n</html>	2018-04-20 09:02:23.75878+00	2018-04-25 09:05:58.060455+00	27	6	t
4849	<!doctype html>\n<html>\n  <head>\n    <title></title>\n    <style>\n     body{                                                             text-align:center;\n         background-image:url(/static/main/images/new_orleans.jpg);        }\n         p{                                                       background-color:rgba(255 ,255 ,255, 0.7);\n         }\n         h1{\n             background-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n         }\n         \n    </style>    \n  </head>\n  <body>\n  <h1>KARIBU  NEW  ORLENS</h1>\n  <P></P>\n      \n    <!-- Photo : /static/main/images/new_orleans.jpg -->\n    <p>New Orlens ni mahali ambako tamaduni mbalimbali zimekutana na kuchanganyika:Wafaransa,watu wa Karibi,watumwa wenye asili ya Afrika,Wahispania kutoka Meksio na Waingereze.</p>\n <p>Mji ni mahali pa muziki hutazamiwa kama mama wa muziki wa Jazz na pia staili ya "Rhythm and blues"iliyokuwa msingi wa"Rock 'n' Roll".Louis Amstrong aliyekuwa mpiga tarumpeta wa Jazz mashuhuri duniani alikuwa mkazi wa mji</p>\n  </body>\n</html>	2018-04-19 11:18:12.070918+00	2018-04-24 09:24:00.381345+00	22	49	t
